isolation, guest mode) blocking device-to-device traffic  \n2. **Different subnet/VLAN** (devices on same SSID name but separated)  \n3. **App-specific port not allowed** (firewall is on, which is good)  \n4. **mDNS/UPnP discovery flakiness** on that router\n\nIf you tell me exactly what you’re connecting (**from this laptop → to what device/app, and which port if known**), I can pinpoint it and give the exact fix without turning security off.","textSignature":"msg_04ec897e4eeabb820169a36b4419608191b8ef5a365861410f"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1653,"output":248,"cacheRead":20480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22381,"cost":{"input":0.00289275,"output":0.003472,"cacheRead":0.003584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00994875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772317503757}}
