ly broken.”\n\nMost likely:\n1. The target device/app is on a different VLAN/guest isolation\n2. The exact app port/protocol is blocked\n3. The target service isn’t listening on LAN\n\nTell me what you’re trying to connect to (exact app/device), and I’ll run the exact port/service test next and give you one fix path.","textSignature":"msg_04ec897e4eeabb820169a36bab630481918deecd0a14ffc6dd"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1054,"output":229,"cacheRead":24448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25731,"cost":{"input":0.0018445,"output":0.003206,"cacheRead":0.0042784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009328900000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772317609031}}
