xists ✅  \n- But OpenClaw is currently bound to **loopback only** (`127.0.0.1`) ⚠️  \n- Gateway service shows **stopped** ⚠️  \n\nThat means: works on this laptop, not reliably from other devices.\n\n### To fully “be the brain” on LAN\nRun these on the laptop:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway start\nopenclaw status --all\n```\n\nIf `status --all` still shows loopback-only bind, we need to set gateway bind to LAN (or all interfaces) in config, then restart gateway.\n\n### Next step (pick one)\n1. **Do it for me now** (I’ll run + verify live)\n2. **Give me exact copy/paste commands only**\n3. **Keep local-only mode** (most secure, no LAN access)\n\nIf you say **1**, I’ll proceed immediately.","textSignature":"msg_04ec897e4eeabb820169a3863bf224819190fa164ed8e0179e"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1560,"output":311,"cacheRead":28928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30799,"cost":{"input":0.00273,"output":0.004354,"cacheRead":0.0050624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0121464}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772324408866}}
